title: You have to see this bride's wedding dress made out of burrito wrappers
text:
A few weeks ago, Taco Bell launched a nationwide contest that generated a lot of social media steam. For $600, lucky couples were able to get married inside the fast food chain's chapel in Las Vegas. Complete with a Taco Bell garter and hot sauce bouquet, it was the wedding of (some) people's dreams.
I made a wedding dress out of burrito wrappers Read more...
